title: Week 10 recap
itunes:title: Week 10 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, Dan Hanzus and Colleen Wolfe – break down all the action from Week 10 of the regular season, including the Patriots beating the Giants in dramatic fashion, and for the first time since 1991. Plus, the Team of ATL (Cardinals) holding off a late-game comeback from the Seahawks, and improving to 7-2.
